snippet.title: Conquests of Camelot: The Search for the Grail - Game Loop Demo (MT-32 music) MS-DOS 1990
snippet.description:
"Conquests of Camelot: The Search for the Grail  "  - loop demo with Roland MT-32 music.
PC MS-DOS.1990
Developed and published by Sierra-On-Line
Music and sounds recorded from a genuine  Roland MT-32 (rev.1 old) device.
Music by  Mark Seibert

Release : PC MS-DOS (1990),  Amiga (1990), Atari ST (1990)
